snippet.title: Heard, Malek, Theron, more, support HFPA’s charity work
snippet.description:
(10 Aug 2018) Amber Heard, Rami Malek, Charlize Theron and Jennifer Garner were among the presenters at the Hollywood Foreign Press Association's star-studded grants dinner. (Aug. 10)
